no\">AMD SEV Topology Logs</span>\n431 |         </div>\n432 |         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-1\">\n433 |           <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/30 uppercase block\">REVIEWS IN PROGRESS</span>\n434 |           <div className=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-mono\">{pendingReviews} <span className=\"text-white/20 text-sm font-sans font-normal\">Pending</span></div>\n435 |           <span className=\"text-[10px] text-amber-400 font-mono\">Awaiting client signature</span>\n436 |         </div>\n437 |       </div>\n438 | \n439 |       {/* 5. MULTI-DIMENSIONAL SEARCH & FILTER BOARD */}\n440 |       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n441 |         <div className=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-stretch xl:items-center\">\n442 |           \n443 |           {/* Main Search Input */}\n444 |           <div className=\"relative flex-grow max-w-xl\">\n445 |             <Search className=\"absolute left-3.5 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-white/30\" />\n446 |             <input \n447 |               type=\"text\" \n448 |               value={searchQuery} \n449 |               onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)} \n450 |               placeholder=\"Search by title, security hash, owner, or details...\"\n451 |               className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] pl-10 pr-10 text-[12px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/25 outline-none focus:border-white/15 focus:bg-white/[0.03] transition-all\"\n452 |             />\n453 |             {searchQuery && (\n454 |               <button onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")} className=\"absolute right-3.5 top-2.5 text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n455 |                 <X className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n456 |               </button>\n457 |             )}\n458 |           </div>\n459 | \n460 |           {/* Controls Right Alignment: Layout Switch & Clear */}\n461 |           <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 self-end xl:self-auto\">\n462 |             {hasActiveFilters && (\n463 |               <button \n464 |                 onClick={handleResetFilters}\n465 |                 className=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-lg border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/5 hover:bg-red-500/10 text-[11px] font-mono font-bold text-red-400 uppercase transition-all flex items-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"\n466 |               >\n467 |                 <X className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n468 |                 <span>Reset Filters</span>\n469 |               </button>\n470 |             )}\n471 | \n472 |             {/* Layout Toggler (Segmented Control style) */}\n473 |             <div className=\"flex items-center rounded-lg border border-white/5 p-1 bg-black/40\">\n474 |               <button \n475 |                 onClick={() => setLayoutMode(\"grid\")}\n476 |                 className={`h-7 px-3.5 rounded-md text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all uppercase ${\n477 |                   layoutMode === \"grid\" ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n478 |                 }`}\n479 |               >\n480 |                 <LayoutGrid className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n481 |                 <span className=\"hidden sm:inline\">Bento Grid</span>\n482 |               </button>\n483 |               <button \n484 |                 onClick={() => setLayoutMode(\"list\")}\n485 |                 className={`h-7 px-3.5 rounded-md text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all uppercase ${\n486 |                   layoutMode === \"list\" ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n487 |                 }`}\n488 |               >\n489 |                 <List className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n490 |                 <span className=\"hidden sm:inline\">Sovereign Ledger</span>\n491 |               </button>\n492 |             </div>\n493 | \n494 |           </div>\n495 |         </div>\n496 | \n497 |         {/* Dropdown Filters row */}\n498 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 border-t border-white/5 pt-4\">\n499 |           \n500 |           {/* Category Dropdown */}\n501 |           <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n502 |             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold block tracking-wider\">Document Category</span>\n503 |             <div className=\"relative\">\n504 |               <select \n505 |                 value={selectedCategory} \n506 |                 onChange={(e) => setSelectedCategory(e.target.value)} \n507 |                 className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-3 pr-8 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white focus:border-white/15 outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n508 |               >\n509 |                 <option value=\"\">ALL CATEGORIES</option>\n510 |                 {CATEGORIES.map(cat => <option key={cat} value={cat}>{cat}</option>)}\n511 |               </select>\n512 |               <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n513 |             </div>\n514 |           </div>\n515 | \n516 |           {/* Project Dropdown */}\n517 |           <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n518 |             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold block tracking-wider\">Related Project</span>\n519 |             <div className=\"relative\">\n520 |               <select \n521 |                 value={selectedProject} \n522 |                 onChange={(e) => setSelectedProject(e.target.value)} \n523 |                 className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-3 pr-8 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white focus:border-white/15 outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n524 |               >\n525 |                 <option value=\"\">ALL PROJECTS</option>\n526 |                 {PROJECTS.map(proj => <option key={proj} value={proj}>{proj}</option>)}\n527 |               </select>\n528 |               <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n529 |             </div>\n530 |           </div>\n531 | \n532 |           {/* Format Dropdown */}\n533 |           <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n534 |             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold block tracking-wider\">Document Type / Format</span>\n535 |             <div className=\"relative\">\n536 |               <select \n537 |                 value={selectedFormat} \n538 |                 onChange={(e) => setSelectedFormat(e.target.value)} \n539 |                 className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-3 pr-8 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white focus:border-white/15 outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n540 |               >\n541 |                 <option value=\"\">ALL FORMATS</option>\n542 |                 {FORMATS.map(fmt => <option key={fmt} value={fmt}>{fmt}</option>)}\n543 |               </select>\n544 |               <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n545 |             </div>\n546 |           </div>\n547 | \n548 |           {/* Status Dropdown */}\n549 |           <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n550 |             <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold block tracking-wider\">Approval Status</span>\n551 |             <div className=\"relative\">\n552 |               <select \n553 |                 value={selectedStatus} \n554 |                 onChange={(e) => setSelectedStatus(e.target.value)} \n555 |                 className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-3 pr-8 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white focus:border-white/15 outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n556 |               >\n557 |                 <option value=\"\">ALL STATUSES</option>\n558 |                 {STATUSES.map(st => <option key={st} value={st}>{st}</option>)}\n559 |               </select>\n560 |               <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-3 top-3 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n561 |             </div>\n562 |           </div>\n563 | \n564 |         </div>\n565 |       </div>\n566 | \n567 |       {/* 6. CONTENT VIEWS (CARD OR TABLE) */}\n568 |       {filteredDocuments.length === 0 ? (\n569 |         \n570 |         /* Empty Search Results state */\n571 |         <div className=\"p-12 text-center rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 backdrop-blur-sm max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-4\">\n572 |           <div className=\"p-4 rounded-full bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 inline-flex text-white/30\">\n573 |             <FolderOpen className=\"w-8 h-8\" />\n574 |           </div>\n575 |           <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n576 |             <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">No Cryptographic Seals Found</h3>\n577 |             <p className=\"text-[12.5px] text-white/40 max-w-sm mx-auto font-sans leading-relaxed\">\n578 |               Your multidimensional filter query did not match any active ledger documents or system architecture plans.\n579 |             </p>\n580 |           </div>\n581 |           <button \n582 |             onClick={handleResetFilters}\n583 |             className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded-lg bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[11px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.15)] inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\"\n584 |           >\n585 |             <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-pulse\" />\n586 |             <span>Restore Master View</span>\n587 |           </button>\n588 |         </div>\n589 | \n590 |       ) : layoutMode === \"grid\" ? (\n591 |         \n592 |         /* A: BENTO GRID VIEW */\n593 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\">\n594 |           {filteredDocuments.map((doc) => (\n595 |             <WorkspaceCard key={doc.id} className=\"flex flex-col h-[280px] justify-between border-white/[0.03] relative group hover:border-[#009DFF]/20 transition-all duration-300\">\n596 |               \n597 |               {/* Document Header details inside card */}\n598 |               <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n599 |                 <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start\">\n600 |                   <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n601 |                     <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-[#009DFF] rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 uppercase\">\n602 |                       {doc.category}\n603 |                     </span>\n604 |                     <span className={`text-[9px] font-mono font-bold border rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 uppercase ${getStatusColor(doc.status)}`}>\n605 |                       {doc.status}\n606 |                     </span>\n607 |                   </div>\n608 |                   <span className={`text-[9px] font-mono font-bold border rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 ${getFormatBadgeColor(doc.format)}`}>\n609 |                     {doc.format}\n610 |                   </span>\n611 |                 </div>\n612 | \n613 |                 <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n614 |                   <h4 className=\"text-[13.5px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors leading-snug line-clamp-2\">\n615 |                     {doc.name}\n616 |                   </h4>\n617 |                   <p className=\"text-[11.5px] text-white/40 font-sans line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\">\n618 |                     {doc.desc}\n619 |                   </p>\n620 |                 </div>\n621 |               </div>\n622 | \n623 |               {/* Document footer & metadata specs inside card */}\n624 |               <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3 mt-4 space-y-3.5\">\n625 |                 <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35\">\n626 |                   <div>\n627 |                     <span className=\"text-white/20 font-bold block text-[8px] uppercase\">OWNER / COMPLIANT</span>\n628 |                     <span className=\"text-white/60 truncate block mt-0.5\">{doc.owner}</span>\n629 |                   </div>\n630 |                   <div className=\"text-right\">\n631 |                     <span className=\"text-white/20 font-bold block text-[8px] uppercase\">VERSION / SIZE</span>\n632 |                     <span className=\"text-white/60 block mt-0.5\">{doc.version} ({doc.size})</span>\n633 |                   </div>\n634 |                 </div>\n635 | \n636 |                 <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n637 |                   <button \n638 |                     onClick={() => setSelectedDoc(doc)}\n639 |                     className=\"h-8 rounded border border-white/5 hover:border-white/15 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold text-white transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"\n640 |                   >\n641 |                     <Eye className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/50\" />\n642 |                     <span>METADATA</span>\n643 |                   </button>\n644 |                   <button \n645 |                     onClick={() => handleSimulatedDownload(doc)}\n646 |                     className=\"h-8 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/15 border border-[#009DFF]/20 hover:border-[#009DFF]/45 text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"\n647 |                   >\n648 |                     <Download className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n649 |                     <span>DOWNLOAD</span>\n650 |                   </button>\n651 |                 </div>\n652 |               </div>\n653 | \n654 |             </WorkspaceCard>\n655 |           ))}\n656 |         </div>\n657 | \n658 |       ) : (\n659 | \n660 |         /* B: SOVEREIGN LEDGER TABLE VIEW */\n661 |         <div className=\"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/10 backdrop-blur-sm\">\n662 |           <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse\">\n663 |             <thead>\n664 |               <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 bg-black/40 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/30 tracking-widest uppercase\">\n665 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">ID</th>\n666 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">DOCUMENT NAME</th>\n667 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">CATEGORY</th>\n668 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">TYPE</th>\n669 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">RELATED PROJECT</th>\n670 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">VERSION</th>\n671 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold\">STATUS</th>\n672 |                 <th className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold text-right\">ACTION</th>\n673 |               </tr>\n674 |             </thead>\n675 |             <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/[0.02] font-mono text-[11.5px] text-white/80\">\n676 |               {filteredDocuments.map((doc) => (\n677 |                 <tr \n678 |                   key={doc.id}\n679 |                   onClick={() => setSelectedDoc(doc)}\n680 |                   className=\"hover:bg-white/[0.02] cursor-pointer transition-colors group\"\n681 |                 >\n682 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-white/40 text-[10.5px] font-bold tracking-wider\">{doc.id}</td>\n683 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors max-w-xs truncate\">\n684 |                     {doc.name}\n685 |                   </td>\n686 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n687 |                     <span className=\"text-[9px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/70 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5\">\n688 |                       {doc.category.toUpperCase()}\n689 |                     </span>\n690 |                   </td>\n691 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n692 |                     <span className={`text-[9px] border rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 ${getFormatBadgeColor(doc.format)}`}>\n693 |                       {doc.format}\n694 |                     </span>\n695 |                   </td>\n696 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-white/40 text-[10.5px] max-w-[150px] truncate\">{doc.project}</td>\n697 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-white/50\">{doc.version}</td>\n698 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4\">\n699 |                     <span className={`text-[9px] font-bold border rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 uppercase ${getStatusColor(doc.status)}`}>\n700 |                       {doc.status}\n701 |                     </span>\n702 |                   </td>\n703 |                   <td className=\"py-3.5 px-4 text-right\" onClick={(e) => e.stopPropagation()}>\n704 |                     <div className=\"flex items-center justify-end gap-2\">\n705 |                       <button \n706 |                         onClick={() => setSelectedDoc(doc)}\n707 |                         className=\"p-1 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n708 |                         title=\"View Metadata Drawer\"\n709 |                       >\n710 |                         <Eye className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n711 |                       </button>\n712 |                       <button \n713 |                         onClick={() => handleSimulatedDownload(doc)}\n714 |                         className=\"p-1 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] hover:border-[#009DFF]/40 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n715 |                         title=\"Simulate Download\"\n716 |                       >\n717 |                         <Download className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n718 |                       </button>\n719 |                     </div>\n720 |                   </td>\n721 |                 </tr>\n722 |               ))}\n723 |             </tbody>\n724 |           </table>\n725 |           \n726 |           {/* Table pagination stats footer */}\n727 |           <div className=\"p-3 border-t border-white/5 bg-black/[0.15] flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 font-mono text-[10px] text-white/40\">\n728 |             <span>SHOWING <strong className=\"text-white/60\">{filteredDocuments.length}</strong> OF <strong className=\"text-white/60\">{PREVIEW_DOCUMENTS.length}</strong> DETERMINISTIC SECURITY SEALS</span>\n729 |             <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] flex items-center gap-1 bg-[#00FFC2]/5 border border-[#00FFC2]/15 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\">\n730 |               <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> HSM MEMORY BUS COMPLIANT\n731 |             </span>\n732 |           </div>\n733 |         </div>\n734 |       )}\n735 | \n736 |       {/* 7. HIGH-FIDELITY SIMULATED DRAG-AND-DROP SECURE UPLOAD */}\n737 |       <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-white/10 bg-[#050505]/10 hover:bg-[#050505]/20 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 select-none mt-4\">\n738 |         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/